<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">People With Disabilities Face Greater Risk of Economic Devastation From COVID-19</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="782" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-1200x782.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="Melissa Baptista checks on her fianc&eacute; Eric McGuire, who is bedridden with several medical conditions and is on oxygen, in Franklin, Massachusetts, on March 25, 2020. Melissa is a nurse at a nearby nursing home and depends on caregivers to take care of his needs, but one caregiver plans to isolate herself because she has a sinus infection and will be tested for coronavirus." itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-1200x782.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-400x261.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-200x130.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-800x522.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-1536x1001.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-2048x1335.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-2400x1565.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="782" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="Melissa Baptista checks on her fianc&eacute; Eric McGuire, who is bedridden with several medical conditions and is on oxygen, in Franklin, Massachusetts, on March 25, 2020. Melissa is a nurse at a nearby nursing home and depends on caregivers to take care of his needs, but one caregiver plans to isolate herself because she has a sinus infection and will be tested for coronavirus." itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-1200x782.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-400x261.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-200x130.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-800x522.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-1536x1001.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-2048x1335.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-2400x1565.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0409-covid-19-disability-1200x782.jpg" loading="lazy">
