<article class="row hentry post-269923 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-news-analysis tag-cares-act tag-covid-19 tag-disabilities tag-disability-rights tag-social-security tag-stimulus-package tag-unemployment tag-universal-basic-income section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-economy" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
