<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/our-responses-to-covid-19-must-center-disability-justice/">Our Responses to COVID-19 Must Center Disability Justice</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Here’s how we can turn these unprecedented and slapdash coronavirus measures into actual disability justice.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/katie-tastrom/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Katie Tastrom</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2020-03-21T14:44:53+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2020-03-21T14:44:53+00:00">March 21, 2020</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
